subSubSection.paragraph:
Description. Holotype , body length 11.0 mm, width 4.0 mm. Variability of size in paratypes : females—8.0– 14.1 x 3.0– 5.6 mm ; males— 7.8–11.9 x 2.7–4.3 mm . Body subparallel, dark brown, dull (
Fig. 8
).

Pronotum (
Fig. 17
) transverse, punctate, punctures same as on head, except space between punctures slightly larger. Anterior margin broadly and deeply emarginate, anterior corners extended. Lateral margin of pronotum slightly and irregularly waved, arcuate before posterior angles. Basal, lateral, and anterior pronotal margins distinctly bordered. Anterior margin medially obliterated.
